oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: A Visit to Bell's Bend
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints);Automobiles;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (green on white) announcing a visit to Bell's Bend, the scene of the latest struggle to preserve biodiversity and historic farmland in the Metro Nashville Area on September 18. Event is part of the American Studies Road Trip Series. Poster features a woodcut of a truck.
